articles.title: Late Sweden winner denies South Africa historic Women’s World Cup draw; Netherlands wins - CNN
articles.description: A battling performance earned Jamaica its first ever point in Women’s World Cup history as the Reggae Girlz secured a 0-0 draw against heavy favorites France.
